      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Forzatura di :                          *
      *                      * - Tipi scadenza da includere            *
      *                      * solo se necessario                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tsc-das (1)    =    0002
                     go to acc-tav-ric-615.
           move      0002                 to   w-tes-tsc-das (1)      .
           perform   vis-tsc-das-000      thru vis-tsc-das-999        .
       acc-tav-ric-615.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
