      *                  * distinta                                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           subtract  w-rig-imp-sdb (1)    from w-tes-imp-ddp (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione totale della distinta       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-tot-dis-000      thru vis-tot-dis-999        .
