      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "Distinta di presentazione non esistente in archivi
      -              "o              "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           perform   box-msg-err-000      thru box-msg-err-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Status di uscita ad errore              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-rou-let-reg      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Uscita                                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     rou-let-reg-999.
       rou-let-reg-350.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se record esistente                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
       rou-let-reg-375.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
